                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su"
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "All creatures within 30 feet of a wanderlust siktempora (but not including the siktempora) gain the effects of the haste spell. If an affected creature doesn\u2019t take a move action to move on its turn, the denied urge to move physically pains that creature, who takes 7d10 damage. A successful DC 20 Will save halves the damage.",
